high_descs: Head to the kitchen to reach the microwave on the right.
Take out the pink egg from the microwave.
Move right to reach the stove.
Put the pink egg on the pot on the stove.
Pick up the pot with the pink egg.
Turn right and head to the bedroom on the right to reach the nightstand next to the bed.
Put the pot with the pink egg on the nightstand.
anns.task_desc: Put the pot with the pink egg on the nightstand.

high_descs: Cross the room to the counter then turn to the microwave on your right.
Get the egg out of the oven.
Turn right towards the stove.
Place the egg on the plate above the stove.
Pick up the plate with the egg on it.
Turn right,  hang a left, then move towards the table in the bedroom.
Place the plate on the table.
anns.task_desc: Pick up the egg from the oven,  put it on the plate,  place it on the table in bedroom.

high_descs: Go into the kitchen and open the microwave door.
Take the egg out of the microwave.
Go to the stove next to the microwave.
Put the egg in the pan on the stove.
Pick up the pan on the stove.
Leave the kitchen, take a left and go into the bedroom on the left and put the pan on the nightstand.
Look at the pan on the nightstand.
anns.task_desc: Put an egg in a pan on the bedroom nightstand.

high_descs: Turn around and go near the microwave.
Take the egg from the microwave oven.
Turn around and go near the pot.
Put the egg on the pot.
Take the pot with egg from the stove.
Turn around and go to the sidetable.
Put the pot with egg on the sidetable.
anns.task_desc: Placed the cooking pot with egg on the side table of the bedroom.

high_descs: Walk across the kitchen over the microwave on the counter.
Open the microwave and pick up the egg inside.
Step slightly to the right over to the pot on the stove top.
Place the egg in the pot that is on the stove.
Pick up the pot with the egg inside of it.
Turn right, walk out of the kitchen, make a left around the corner, and go into the bedroom over to the sidetable next to the bed.
Place the pot with the egg in it on the sidetable next to the bed.
anns.task_desc: Serve an Egg, which was in the microwave, with a Pot on the SideTable of the bedroom.

high_descs: Go forward to the microwave in the kitchen.
Take the egg out of the microwave.
Go to the pot on the right.
Put the egg in the pot on the stove.
Pick up the pot with the egg in it.
Go right and then turn left into a bedroom and go to the sidetable.
Put the pot with the egg in it on the sidetable.
anns.task_desc: Put the egg in the pot on the nightstand in the bedroom.
